Download and set class path for following jars with their versions
jaf-1.1.1 - activation.jar
javamail-1.4.4 - mail.jar
mysql-connector-j-8.0.31.jar
smtp.jar

The last jar is to be downloaded separately
fakeSMTP-2.0.jar 
Link: http://nilhcem.com/FakeSMTP/index.html
To run this server, simply double click and set listening port as 9090 and start server through GUI
